I usually don't say much about stuff like this because I'm someone who likes to speak through action and I'm not the best around arguments and debates n shit. I just like to share love and positivity.
But my good friends DJ King Tech of the @worldfamouswakeupshow @shade45 and Alex Tse called me after work on a Friday late night and I was in a talking mood. There are many takes on what's going on with Asians in America right now, this is ours.
Peace

node.text: I’m stoked to be a part of @Canoo’s Multi-Purpose Delivery Vehicle global reveal. This vehicle is literally the future. It’s fully electric, adaptable and designed for the people. I love that @canoo is thinking about us on the ground and helping the grind by bridging the old with the new. It was designed to maximize any small or big business’s productivity with more storage, utility and technology for a better and lower total cost of ownership than other options on the market. Check out the full reveal I participated in via link in IG Stories. #Canoo #CanooPartner

hi y'all. i made these short movies before the pandemic wanting to bring attention to and support small businesses, starting with three friends in creative fields. sitting here now 8 months later makes me think how much more poignant these videos are now as we are losing the whole fabric of small business in our communities where everyone from chefs to barbers to tattoo artists to ceramicists to many more are trying to figure out how to figure it out..
i don't wanna get too deep because when we filmed these it wasn't really about that. but it just hit me. it is deep. thanks for hearing my thoughts and I'd like to introduce you to my dear friends at @elysianbarbershop , @pot_la , and @thetattoogallery 
enjoy!
oh yeah, this is video 1 of like 5. each next video released will go deep into each of their lives.
this is the intro.
thanks to the filmmakers and square for making these with me.

node.text: Thanks to all of y'all who’ve shared your love for the Plant-Based Kogi Dog made with @FieldRoast. Now we’re also releasing a line of stadium inspired clothing to go with the dog, made in collaboration with Studio Number One. Just head to select @kogibbq trucks June 26th-27th from 11:30am-2pm to get some free shirts, hats, and more when you order “The Home Run”. I can't wait for you to try it and get free stuff! #MakeTasteHappen

node.text:
FINALLY I CAN TELL Y'ALL: Broken Bread got picked up for a Season 2 and it is coming! I'm getting my body in camera shape as I write this...lol. And just like season 1, we want to hear from you about anyone doing the good work on the ground out there against all odds, building equity through food and wellness, and spreading love and light. So if you know anyone for the new season where we can shine a light and amplify their voices please Share it right in the comments and tag #brokenbread. The team and I will look at every one.
Please leave as much contact info for your suggestions as you can in comments or just DM me.
Use #BrokenBread so we can track it.
Love you and LFG!
@brokenbread_

node.text:
For an introvert like me, it's been a blessing to build with all of you here on these channels of social media and express ideas, have convos, share things. You all are truly my best friends. It's been a wonderful chapter of my life the last ten years or so. Love you.
And this restaurant and all that it represents is a dedication to all of that.
💜
#nationalbestfriendsday
#nationalbestfriendday 
#bestfriend
